        "id": 261574,
        "name": "",
        "username": "PiCob",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/picob/{size}/589_2.png",
        "created_at": "2025-02-19T10:31:01.925Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Maybe one of the topics below already covers your feature request?</p>\n<aside class=\"quote quote-modified\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"36949\">\n  <div class=\"title\">\n    <div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n    <img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/meteor0id/48/55420_2.png\" class=\"avatar\">\n    <div class=\"quote-title__text-content\">\n      <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/ability-to-stop-sharing-your-profile-with-people/36949/\">Ability to stop sharing your profile with people</a> <a class=\"badge-category__wrapper \" href=\"/c/feature-requests/17\"><span data-category-id=\"17\" style=\"--category-badge-color: #83B72A; --category-badge-text-color: #FFFFFF;\" data-drop-close=\"true\" class=\"badge-category --style-square \" title=\"Post your ideas here for new features and functionality for the Signal app.\"><span class=\"badge-category__name\">Feature Requests</span></span></a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n    Stop sharing means: they will keep seeing the profile picture and name which you were using the moment you stopped sharing - they wonâ€™t receive updates of your profile name, status or picture. \nAs it stands today anyone you were once in a group with will keep seeing every new pucture you set for yourself, but you have no idea who or how many people are seeing your new profile picture. \nWe need two things: \n\nan overview of people who we are sharing our profile with\na way to stop sharing the profiâ€¦\n  </blockquote>\n</aside>\n\n<aside class=\"quote\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"36962\">\n  <div class=\"title\">\n    <div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n    <img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/herohtar/48/43780_2.png\" class=\"avatar\">\n    <div class=\"quote-title__text-content\">\n      <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/improved-profile-sharing-controls/36962\">Improved profile sharing controls</a> <a class=\"badge-category__wrapper \" href=\"/c/feature-requests/17\"><span data-category-id=\"17\" style=\"--category-badge-color: #83B72A; --category-badge-text-color: #FFFFFF;\" data-drop-close=\"true\" class=\"badge-category --style-square \" title=\"Post your ideas here for new features and functionality for the Signal app.\"><span class=\"badge-category__name\">Feature Requests</span></span></a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n    There have been multiple requests that revolve around profile sharing controls, and while they are all slightly different, they have a significant amount of overlap and result in duplicate discussions. Due to the timespan of the threads and related discussion, rather than a confusing merge of all the posts, I am simply going to close the other topics and link them here. Any discussion relating to profile sharing can be continued in this topic.\n  </blockquote>\n</aside>\n",
