        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/scoupland/{size}/50708_2.png",
        "created_at": "2025-02-22T21:13:10.168Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Thank you for sharing those links, I had a good read.</p>\n<p>They are all centering around profile sharing however my request is more focused around group interaction.</p>\n<p>I specifically want to stop people in a group that I donâ€™t know from messaging me, or in the use case I suggested, an under 18 year old in a group, where it would be safeguarding concern for them to be messaged by another person that doesnt have DBS clearence (police check).</p>\n<p>Thanks again, hope this gets some traction.</p>",
